directions: Stir spaghetti squash, tomatoes, chicken broth, chicken, bell pepper, salt, sugar, parsley, basil, oregano, garlic powder, and onion powder together in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low for 5 to 6 hours.
ingredients: 12 ounces spaghetti squash, peeled, seeded, and cut into 3-inch pieces
title: Slow Cooker Spaghetti Squash Chicken Soup
